-# Interpersonal Communication (التَّوَاصُلُ الشَّخْصِيُّ)
-
-## 1) Vocabulary List (15 Words)
-
-| # | Arabic (with harakah) | English |
-|---|---|---|
-| 1 | تَعَارُفٌ | introduction |
-| 2 | رَأْيٌ | opinion |
-| 3 | مُوَافَقَةٌ | agreement |
-| 4 | اِخْتِلَافٌ | disagreement |
-| 5 | اِحْتِرَامٌ | respect |
-| 6 | مُجَامَلَةٌ | compliment |
-| 7 | اِمْتِنَانٌ | gratitude |
-| 8 | اِعْتِذَارٌ | apology |
-| 9 | تَفَاهُمٌ | understanding |
-| 10 | تَعَاوُنٌ | cooperation |
-| 11 | مُنَاقَشَةٌ | discussion |
-| 12 | ثِقَةٌ | trust |
-| 13 | آدَابٌ | etiquette |
-| 14 | تَأْثِيرٌ | influence |
-| 15 | قِيَمٌ | values |
-
-## 2) 10 Essential Sentences
-
-| # | Arabic | English | Transliteration |
-|---|---|---|---|
-| 1 | يُسْعِدُنِي التَّعَارُفُ عَلَيْكَ. | Pleased to meet you. | yusʿidunī al-taʿārufu ʿalayka. |
-| 2 | فِي رَأْيِي هَذَا الاِقْتِرَاحُ مُنَاسِبٌ. | In my opinion this proposal is suitable. | fī raʾyī hādhā al-iqtirāḥu munāsibun. |
-| 3 | أُوَافِقُكَ فِي هَذِهِ النُّقْطَةِ. | I agree with you on this point. | uwāfiquka fī hādhihi al-nuqṭati. |
-| 4 | أَحْتَرِمُ رَأْيَكَ وَلَكِنْ لَدَيَّ وِجْهَةٌ أُخْرَى. | I respect your view but I have another one. | aḥtarimu raʾyaka walākin ladayya wijhatun ukhrā. |
-| 5 | شُكْرًا لَكَ عَلَى التَّعَاوُنِ. | Thank you for the cooperation. | shukran laka ʿalā al-taʿāwuni. |
-| 6 | أَعْتَذِرُ عَنْ سُوءِ الفَهْمِ السَّابِقِ. | I apologize for the previous misunderstanding. | aʿtadhiru ʿan sūʾi al-fahmi al-sābiqi. |
